      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Older poor-condition example being sold honestly as-is. This is not a clean driver and should be viewed as a project, repair candidate, or possible parts car depending on your plans. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, aging throughout, and deferred maintenance, and assume it will need mechanical attention before it can be considered dependable. Best suited for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and is prepared for the work involved.",
