    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it offers a lot of potential at an accessible price point. A straightforward choice for buyers who prioritize budget, utility, and room to make it their own.",
